M|algorithmic-art|Algorithmic philosophies are computational aesthetic movements that are then expressed through code. Output .md files (philosophy), .html files (interactive viewer), and .js files (generative algorith
M|algorithmic-art|This happens in two steps:
M|algorithmic-art|1. Algorithmic Philosophy Creation (.md file)
M|algorithmic-art|2. Express by creating p5.js generative art (.html + .js files)
M|algorithmic-art|First, undertake this task:
M|algorithmic-art|To begin, create an ALGORITHMIC PHILOSOPHY (not static images or templates) that will be interpreted through:
M|algorithmic-art|- Computational processes, emergent behavior, mathematical beauty
M|algorithmic-art|- Seeded randomness, noise fields, organic systems
M|algorithmic-art|- Particles, flows, fields, forces
M|algorithmic-art|- Parametric variation and controlled chaos
M|algorithmic-art|- What is received: Some subtle input or instructions by the user to take into account, but use as a foundation; it should not constrain creative freedom.
M|algorithmic-art|- What is created: An algorithmic philosophy/generative aesthetic movement.
M|algorithmic-art|- What happens next: The same version receives the philosophy and EXPRESSES IT IN CODE - creating p5.js sketches that are 90% algorithmic generation, 10% essential parameters.
M|algorithmic-art|Consider this approach:
M|algorithmic-art|- Write a manifesto for a generative art movement
M|algorithmic-art|- The next phase involves writing the algorithm that brings it to life
M|algorithmic-art|The philosophy must emphasize: Algorithmic expression. Emergent behavior. Computational beauty. Seeded variation.
M|algorithmic-art|**Name the movement** (1-2 words): "Organic Turbulence" / "Quantum Harmonics" / "Emergent Stillness"
M|algorithmic-art|**Articulate the philosophy** (4-6 paragraphs - concise but complete):
M|algorithmic-art|To capture the ALGORITHMIC essence, express how this philosophy manifests through:
M|algorithmic-art|- Computational processes and mathematical relationships?
M|algorithmic-art|- Noise functions and randomness patterns?
M|algorithmic-art|- Particle behaviors and field dynamics?
M|algorithmic-art|- Temporal evolution and system states?
M|algorithmic-art|- Parametric variation and emergent complexity?
