M|algorithmic-art|**THE ESSENTIAL PRINCIPLE**:
M|algorithmic-art|The concept is a **subtle, niche reference embedded within the algorithm itself** - not always literal, always sophisticated. Someone familiar with the subject should feel it intuitively, while others
