M|algorithmic-art|2. **Create an algorithmic philosophy** (4-6 paragraphs) describing the computational approach
M|algorithmic-art|3. **Implement it in code** - Build the algorithm that expresses this philosophy
M|algorithmic-art|4. **Design appropriate parameters** - What should be tunable?
M|algorithmic-art|5. **Build matching UI controls** - Sliders/inputs for those parameters
